snippet.title: Finger Road - Official release trailer
snippet.description:
A time killer game with minimalist approach. Try to keep your finger on the road and avoid obstacles. There are 90 levels, but that's not all. If you complete the game, you unlock Endless mode. There, you can compete on leaderboards. You can also customize the game using the in-game currency. There are several powerups to help you out!

Download for free:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.phisolutions.FingerRoad&hl=en

Follow us on twitter:
https://twitter.com/FingerRoad_Game



Music:
"EDM Detection Mode" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
